.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-EXPORT-CSV" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-export-csv \- export ledger entries as CSV
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-export-csv
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.RB [ --account
.IR address ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Writes ledger entries from the active wallet to stdout in CSV format.
Entries are sorted oldest-first.
.PP
Columns:
.nf
id, account, ts, direction, amount_msat, amount_sat,
peer, payment_hash, message, note
.fi
.TP
.B --limit N
Maximum number of rows to export (default 10000).
.TP
.B --account ADDRESS
Filter to a single account by its on-chain address.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success (outputs header-only CSV if the database is absent).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-backup (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-stats (1)
